      &lt;img alt="An image of Elon Musk in a tuxedo making an odd face. The background is red with weight scales on it." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jKXK_tnjtKjEdRmbVlPrhdXy-kk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73725415/VRG_Illo_STK022_K_Radtke_Musk_Scales_2.0.jpg" /&gt;
